title: What’s New and What’s Next at Disneyland Resort in 2017
text:
This year is already shaping up to be a big one at the Disneyland Resort with the return of the Main Street Electrical Parade at Disneyland park and the popular Lunar New Year celebration at Disney California Adventure park. And there’s so much more ahead! Take a look …

What are you most excited for at the Disneyland Resort in 2017? Tell us in the comments!
